Tips for a great family trip to Maui!
-Book a condo with @kbmresortrentals 
-Their customer service is top notch 🙌🏼
Save: 20% with code ANGELA20 until 7/7 
-We love to stay at Honua Kai in Ka’anapali. You get to enjoy all the amenities of a resort with much more space than a traditional hotel room. 
-Our condo had a full kitchen and washer & dryer, which comes in so convenient for family trips! 
-Once you get into the airport, make sure to stop by Costco. They have a ton of local Hawaiian items that aren’t available at Mainland Costco!
-Stop by all the local spots and support local businesses. 
-Feel free to shout out your favorite Hawaiian businesses in the comments!
